I may be wrong but I don't think someone wanders past the EQ box and says &quot;maybe I'll try that out&quot;. I think it is people who have a friend who plays and talks them into trying it out and that friend takes them through the &quot;basic training&quot; that is learning the game. There is so much to it that cannot be summed up in a manual that people will sit down and read before logging in the first time. <br>
<br>
